PrecisAmendment to Order in Council P.C. 1998-1530 of August 26, 1998, which corrects the legal description of the 42.03 hectares of land on CANOE LAKE INDIAN RESERVE NO. 165 in Saskatchwan, described in Schedule II thereto, whose administration and control was thereby transferred to the Province of Saskatchewan for roadway purposes.
